GEORGE MUSE CLOTHING CO., Objecting Creditor, Appellant, v. William E. RICHARDSON, Bankrupt, Appellee. No. 6646. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Oct. 7, 1932. *1028Edwin MeKiguey Pearee and Houston White, both of Atlanta, Ga., for appellant. Ralph H. Pharr, of Atlanta, Ga., for ap-pellee.

Before BRYAN, FOSTER, and WALKER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment is affirmed.
